  "method": [
    "Cut chicken breasts into slices horizontally.",
    "Mix together all the ingredients. Then put the chicken in it to",
    "marinate and mix well. Marinate for up to 9-10 hours in the",
    "refrigerator.",
    "Take the chicken out, and sprinkle salt on the chicken slices.",
    "Heat oil in a frying pan, and heat chicken for around 2-3 minutes on",
    "high heat. Turnover and cook the other side until it is well seared.",
    "Cover seared breasts with foil then set aside.",
    "Cook the onions and peppers on high heat. Spread the peppers and",
    "onions in the pan for around 2 minutes.",
    "Put vegetables and cook for 2-3 minutes.",
    "Cut chicken pieces, and serve with warm tortillas, onions and",
    "peppers, shredded cheese, guacamole, salsa, and iceberg lettuce,",
    "whatever you like."
